<section class="section container">
	<div class="sectionHeading">Program Education Outcomes</div>
	<div class="sectionContent">
		<ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
			<li class="list-group-item py-4"><strong>1. </strong>To provide students with the fundamentals of Engineering Sciences with more emphasis in Electrical Engineering by way of analyzing and exploiting engineering challenges.</li>
			<li class="list-group-item py-4"><strong>2. </strong>To train students with good scientific and engineering knowledge so as to comprehend, analyze, design and create novel products and solutions for the real life problems.</li>
			<li class="list-group-item py-4"><strong>3.</strong>To inculcate professional and ethical attitude, effective communication skills, teamwork skills, multidisciplinary approach, entrepreneurial thinking and an ability to relate engineering issues with social issues.</li>
			<li class="list-group-item py-4"><strong>4. </strong>To provide students with an academic environment aware of excellence, leadership, written ethical codes and guidelines, and the self-motivated life-long learning needed for a successful professional career.</li>
			<li class="list-group-item py-4"><strong>5. </strong>To prepare students to excel in Industry and Higher education by Educating Students along with High moral values and Knowledge.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>